_examples.ISO_639_3_eng:
Kelvin — cannot be below absolute zero:

```json
{
	"_prop": {
		"SI_base": true,
		"SI_factor": 1.0,
		"UCUM_code": "K",
		"unit_range": { "_min-inclusive": 0 }
	}
}
```

Percent — bounded to [0, 100]:

```json
{
	"_prop": {
		"SI_factor": 0.01,
		"UCUM_code": "%",
		"unit_range": { "_min-inclusive": 0, "_max-inclusive": 100 }
	}
}
```
